  "detailed_description": "<h1>Coming soon - Grunn!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Tomscape is an online role-playing game in which you slap rats, frogs, and other players to become the coolest.<br><br><i>Note: a working internet connection is required to play this game.</i><br><br><i>Disclaimer: There's a very slight chance the game won't work as it's created by an inexperienced networking programmer, of course feel free to refund the game if it does not work for you!</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1135120/extras/2ea2542a9d5b02a340d07e76c9b816b1.poster.avif?t=1711359086\" width=560 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1135120/extras/2ea2542a9d5b02a340d07e76c9b816b1.webm?t=1711359086\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1135120/extras/2ea2542a9d5b02a340d07e76c9b816b1.mp4?t=1711359086\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 10-60 minutes of playtime (and more if you like to grind for experience).<br></li><li> Play online with other people! <br></li><li> Defeat sheep, frogs, rats, guards to level up and become a stronger person.<br></li><li> Chill in the hot springs.<br></li><li> Chat with other players, or yourself.</li></ul><br><strong>Controls</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Left mouse button to move and attack.<br></li><li> Return key to toggle the chat, and then just use your keyboard to talk!</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1135120/extras/c350ac25322f0cc81d29044611c576b9.avif?t=1711359086\" width=200 height=70 /></span><br>Sokpop makes a new game every two weeks!<br>Subscribe for 3$ per month at ",
